<div class='flex flex-col gap-6'>
  <div class='flex items-center justify-between'>
    <div class='grid gap-1'>
      <h1 class='font-heading text-2xl font-semibold dark:text-white'>Getting
        Started</h1>
      <p class='text-base text-muted-foreground'>Learn the fundamentals of
        entrepreneurship and get your startup journey started.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6'>
    <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
      <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-4'>1. Identify Your
        Idea</h3>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground mb-4'>
        Start by finding a problem worth solving. Look for pain points in your
        own life or observe market gaps.
      </p>
      <ul class='space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground'>
        <li>• Brainstorm problems you encounter daily</li>
        <li>• Research market trends and opportunities</li>
        <li>• Validate ideas through customer interviews</li>
        <li>• Use our AI tools to generate and refine ideas</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
      <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-4'>2. Validate Your
        Concept</h3>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground mb-4'>
        Test your idea with real potential customers before building anything.
      </p>
      <ul class='space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground'>
        <li>• Create a landing page to test interest</li>
        <li>• Conduct surveys and interviews</li>
        <li>• Build a minimum viable product (MVP)</li>
        <li>• Analyze feedback and iterate</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
      <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-4'>3. Build Your
        Business Model</h3>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground mb-4'>
        Define how your business will create, deliver, and capture value.
      </p>
      <ul class='space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground'>
        <li>• Identify your target customers</li>
        <li>• Define your value proposition</li>
        <li>• Map out revenue streams</li>
        <li>• Use our AI business model generator</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
      <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-4'>4. Plan Your
        Finances</h3>
      <p class='text-muted-foreground mb-4'>
        Create realistic financial projections and funding strategies.
      </p>
      <ul class='space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground'>
        <li>• Estimate startup costs</li>
        <li>• Project revenue and expenses</li>
        <li>• Plan your funding strategy</li>
        <li>• Use our financial modeling tools</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class='bg-card p-6 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-border'>
    <h3 class='text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-4'>Next Steps</h3>
    <div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4'>
      <a
        href='/pages/learn/courses'
        class='flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg border border-border hover:bg-muted transition-colors'
      >
        <div
          class='w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 flex items-center justify-center'
        >
          {{lucide 'BookOpen' 'w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400'}}
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class='font-medium text-foreground'>Take a Course</p>
          <p class='text-sm text-muted-foreground'>Deepen your knowledge</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a
        href='/pages/learn/tutorials'
        class='flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg border border-border hover:bg-muted transition-colors'
      >
        <div
          class='w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-green-100 dark:bg-green-900 flex items-center justify-center'
        >
          {{lucide 'PlayCircle' 'w-5 h-5 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400'}}
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class='font-medium text-foreground'>Watch Tutorials</p>
          <p class='text-sm text-muted-foreground'>Step-by-step guidance</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a
        href='/pages/dashboard/startup/overview'
        class='flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-lg border border-border hover:bg-muted transition-colors'
      >
        <div
          class='w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900 flex items-center justify-center'
        >
          {{lucide 'Plus' 'w-5 h-5 text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400'}}
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class='font-medium text-foreground'>Start a Project</p>
          <p class='text-sm text-muted-foreground'>Apply what you've learned</p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>